  "A noble gas, particularly regarding electrons": "",
  "A positively charged ion based on the prevailing evidence": "",
  "A negatively charged ion formed when an atom gains electrons": "",
  "A neutral atom, particularly regarding define": "",
  "Nonmetals gain electrons to achieve a full outer shell, forming anions: Cl⁻, O²⁻, N³⁻. The added electrons create a net negative charge.": "",
